Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.48,0:02:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第62话 高深莫测的阿椿咒术
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么抵抗都是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖的\N成为妖怪的饵食吧  犬夜叉!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不用铁碎牙就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种杂碎妖怪  单手就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴硬的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞刃血爪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要忘了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇的性命还在我的手上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题…没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  去帮助犬夜叉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样戈薇会撑不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…椿不论犬夜叉赢或输
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.26,0:03:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都打算咒杀戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.49,0:03:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  非得切断椿的咒术不可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒椿  或打倒咒术媒介的式神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇在倒下去之前曾说过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被不知名的东西咬了一口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  那可能就是黑巫女的式神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该就是那条蛇没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  麻烦你掩护我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破魔符吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别做无谓的挣扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢!我的咒术是不会破解的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不清楚情况的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:05:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抵抗只会延长戈薇的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说到不如
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就送戈薇上路算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  振作点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吵…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪…谁在叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  快点起床
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想睡到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:05:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会在这边的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你睡迷糊了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要吃早餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.35,0:06:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连早安都不会说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是什么时候回到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有去过什么地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那边的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五百年前过去的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是进入隐密的井里面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到有很多妖怪的战国时代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你进去过那口井里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是已经来回好几次了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连犬夜叉都有来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:06:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们连犬夜叉都忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷  你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里长着狗耳朵的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐  今天向学校请假比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是睡迷糊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐  快迟到了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的事情  全部都是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点精神都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在烦恼什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是跟男朋友处的不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了!你们还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:07:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男生的事情对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  果然不是在作梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B班的北条同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是爱吃醋又粗鲁任性的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇你脚踏两条船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇真有精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还搞不懂状况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是突然回到原来的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日暮同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着念下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考试快到了  别再发呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考试
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错…我必须要准备考试
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我原本的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是我的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日暮同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我听说\N日暮同学没什么精神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.29,0:09:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个对身体很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踩踩看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是哪里不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得这样下去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要很多小孩呢\N讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶  买四魂之玉给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起这个四魂之玉的由来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.95,0:09:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要从战国时代…\N走吧  奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蚋  我觉得自己怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许许多多的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在脑海里转来转去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好像有一件非做不可的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要回忆起来的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愈来愈模糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然一直有一种不可以再这样下去的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但到底是什么事非做不可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时感受到的脖子的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也渐渐的习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,思绪也变的无法止息了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要焦急
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么觉得不安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了  日暮同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  抱歉  北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日暮同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总算来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要试试看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为了这个而来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  那个标靶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好的瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,架式不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你的集中力不够
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问…请问你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉又会丧命的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:13:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬…犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还无法离开这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是说这个的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界是你的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:13:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么还能动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的集中力不够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你已经能耐住咒缚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谣传你是桔梗转世
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎不全是唬人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是真正的桔梗  刚才那一箭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该能确实的命中我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底你不过是桔梗的赝品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这人真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是其他人!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢的家伙  这么急着找死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去  戈薇会支持不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  能再稍微撑一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会努力试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那两人大卸八块
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会让你被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我闪开  杂碎!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了  椿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死心吧  椿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为这样就能切断咒术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诅咒的效力还存在着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是杀了式神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你们几个也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有妖怪在她的体内吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母  留在戈薇的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,式神…该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕!这些妖怪全都是诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才发现太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,式神!咬断那女人的脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺取四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会输给你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将式神打回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是咒术反噬!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和桔梗一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那个时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会被这小丫头给…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉被净化了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎片取出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:19:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住  臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂碎片就那样给她?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  马上就能取回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给黑巫女一个雪耻的机会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还蛮体贴的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耗尽力量了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饲养的妖怪统统死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就只差一步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只要有这颗四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能让我的力量更加强大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我一定会打倒他们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好觉悟吧  犬夜叉  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇十分疲倦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.23,0:21:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是不得已的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她一直和咒术抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.73,0:21:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我在一起老是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我喜欢和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:21:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:37.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
